BASH is Ubiquitous: BASH is everywhere.                                       
BASH is Self-sufficent: Avoid dependencies.                                   
BASH is Extendable: Can call other commands for extra functionality.          
BASH is Well-known: Most Linux Administrators have some familiarity.          
